casebody.data:
Joseph Wayne HEXOM, petitioner,
v.
MINNESOTA. No. 15-1052. Supreme Court of the United States June 28, 2016.

On petition for writ of certiorari to the Court of Appeals of Minnesota. Petition for writ of certiorari granted. Judgment vacated, and case remanded to the Court of Appeals of Minnesota for further consideration in light of Birchfield v. North Dakota, 579 U.S. ----, 136 S.Ct. 2160, ---L.Ed.2d ---- (2016).
